Alembic migration environment for twelvewin.

Use Flask-Migrate with the Python 3.12 environment:

    export FLASK_APP=manage.py
    TWELVEWIN_DISABLE_ANALYZER=1 flask db migrate -m "describe schema change"
    TWELVEWIN_DISABLE_ANALYZER=1 flask db upgrade

The initial baseline revision is:

    migrations/versions/33e7716425a6_baseline_schema.py

It captures the current Flask-SQLAlchemy metadata. Before applying it to an
existing production database, back up the database and verify that the baseline
matches the real schema.
